{"build_type":"executable","description":"Rename one function symbol AND every call site across the whole package graph. Request (argv[1]): {\"rename-function-across-packages\":{\"from\":\"<old_symbol>\",\"to\":\"<new_symbol>\",\"roots\":[\"<dir>\",...]}}. Enumerates the universe under roots, collects all package paths, and applies the rename via the proven ed_all_packages machinery (g_rename_match maps from->true, g_rename_to=to). Self-enumerates from roots (no explicit path list passed in), matching build-graph/xref/rename-package. Emits {status, from, to} on stdout. Bad request (no argv, unparseable, no arg object, no from/to/roots) -> clean JSON {error}, no crash. Reuses parse_argument_vector_json_request, locate_named_member_inside_mapping, add_str_field, encode_boolean_payload_document_value, attach_named_member_inside_mapping, enumerate_universe_packages, count_members_inside_container_value, begin_empty_sequence_document_value, collect_universe_paths_into_array, ed_all_packages, begin_empty_mapping_document_value, emit_result_object_onto_standard_output.","module_name":"rename-function-across-universe-packages","package_name":"rename-function-across-universe-packages","module_globals":[{"global_name":"g_rename_match","global_type":"i64","global_init":"0"},{"global_name":"g_rename_to","global_type":"i64","global_init":"0"}],"function_definitions":{"rename-function-across-universe-packages":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"__argc","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"__argv","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_from","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"from"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_to","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string"